{"tid":974384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外媒漫畫諷刺中國對南海主權主張「九段線」 誇張地延伸到月球   對台灣觀念超正確！","createTime":"2019-01-08T23:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T09:30:40.000Z","uid":35790,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ac340e91d61e3671596572a6ec15185966aa5f08","tid":974384,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T23:28:01.000Z","msg":"外媒漫畫諷刺中國管到外太空 對台灣觀念超正確！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpzUxYhY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpzUxYhY.jpg&h=f17f3fd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外媒刊登一幅漫畫，把中國主張南海主權的「九段線」誇張地延伸到月球，諷刺中國管很寬。（圖擷取自新加坡海峽時報）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美、中兩國貿易戰休兵90以來，展開第一回合面對面磋商的同時，7日美國海軍一艘飛彈驅逐艦駛入中國聲稱擁有主權的西沙群島海域，中國除立刻警告驅離，中國外交部也發聲明要求美方停止挑釁。對此，有外媒用漫畫諷刺中國管很寬，把月球劃入中國領土範圍內，大酸中國管到外太空去。<br />\n<br />\n美國海軍麥康貝爾號飛彈驅逐艦（USS McCampbell）7日進入中國南海西沙群島（美方聲為帕拉塞爾群島），並進入趙述島、東島和永興島12海里以內的海域；該海域一向被中國列為領海，但美方認為是「自由航行」，航行主要是挑戰中國「過分的海權主張」，並依照國際法保存這一航道的暢通。中國外交部對此火冒三丈，事後更發表聲明，指控美方侵犯中國主權，還要求美方不要再挑釁。<br />\n<br />\n對此，新加坡《海峽時報》和美國《紐約時報》刊登一幅漫畫，諷刺地把中國對南海主權主張的「九段線」，誇張地連月球都包含在內，意在諷刺中國「住海邊、管很寬」，可以管到外太空去；另外，漫畫中清楚的把台灣畫在中國旁邊，觀念也非常正確的沒有把台灣列為中國領土裡。<br />\n<br />\n台灣網友見狀紛紛笑稱，「管到外太空卻管不到台灣，玻璃又碎啦！」、「中國玻璃心又碎啦 玻璃類股股價大漲！」、「<span style=\"color: red;\">嫦娥是中國人，月球是中國自古不可分割的一部分！」、</span>「酸度真的突破天際！（筆記）」、「哈哈哈哈 全世界都知道中國的德性哈哈哈哈」、「比較好笑的是台灣不是紅色 真是超酸！」、「<span style=\"color: red;\">台灣沒有畫紅色 又可以看中國人崩潰了 超爽」</span>、「這張很讚 我存起來了」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2665906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2665906&d=k9ZiUbGtGu0WCTuOQXTcBwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7f9d96aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2665906&h=d452dfa8\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2665906</a>"},{"pid":"5e91d4d0c4fb9a78474e12189faca2fa1b0960fe","tid":974384,"uid":60366,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T23:30:51.000Z","msg":"重點係撚型<br />\n即係串緊中國打飛機"},{"pid":"467a5c74c0403818086f23ee58993a07c6b3a84d","tid":974384,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e91d4d0c4fb9a78474e12189faca2fa1b0960fe","tid":974384,"uid":60366,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T23:30:51.000Z","msg":"重點係撚型<br />\n即係串緊中國打飛機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T23:34:05.000Z","msg":"不過尿道閉塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6effdf8b21fedab36debbcef3111cf760b2a8f","tid":974384,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"467a5c74c0403818086f23ee58993a07c6b3a84d","tid":974384,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e91d4d0c4fb9a78474e12189faca2fa1b0960fe","tid":974384,"uid":60366,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T23:30:51.000Z","msg":"重點係撚型<br />\n即係串緊中國打飛機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T23:34:05.000Z","msg":"不過尿道閉塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T23:40:11.000Z","msg":"前列腺塞咗"},{"pid":"de9df1ce08b85742fa07c5dea4409664f10c167d","tid":974384,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba6effdf8b21fedab36debbcef3111cf760b2a8f","tid":974384,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"467a5c74c0403818086f23ee58993a07c6b3a84d","tid":974384,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"